attributeSource.infoString2: Coldwell Banker Residential Brokerage - 400 North/Lake Lanier

data.description: Awesome outdoor entertaining in the perfect North Hall neighborhood ! NO HOA !!! Hard to find these features at this price; outdoor oasis complete with inground salt water pool, lots of pool decking for furniture and a built in bar. A separate covered space for cooking with a smoker and collapsible work table for prepping and strings of outdoor lights. Hot tub and garden area. Large screened porch with vaulted ceiling off of the kitchen plus a separate large grilling/sun deck that overlooks the pool area below. Updated kitchen with quartz countertops & pull out drawers. Tiled shower, in the master bath along with double bowl vanity, stackable washer & dryer & a walk in closet. The basement has a workshop, finished bath, rec/family room with fireplace, & a flex room that could be an office or another bedroom. This is a very small established neighborhood that is located close to Lake Lanier and the Olympic Rowing Venue for enjoying lake activities or food truck Fridays. Located close to shopping, restaurants & downtown Gainesville area as well as NE GA hospital. You have to see this one in person to appreciate !
